    <p>I am Zab, I have been in the accounting industry for 6 years. I graduated with a Bachelor’s Degree in Accounting Technology in 2017. I am very hardworking and dedicated. Passionate about my job, I always aim to produce a positive output. I am also a quick learner and can easily adapt to new computer software. I believe that you can do everything through hard work and perseverance — “You can teach skills but not attitude.”</p>
